                    <msContents>
                        <summary>Commentary on the hilkhot ha-Rif by Yishmaʻel ben
                            Ḥakhmon</summary>
                        <msItem n="1" xml:id="MS_Marsh_499_a">
                            <locus>ff. 1r-83v</locus>
                            <author ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/36811473">
                                <persName key="person_36811473">Yishmaʻel ben
                                    Ḥakhmon </persName>
                                <persName xml:lang="he"> ישמעאל בן
                                    חכמון</persName>
                            </author>
                            <title>Commentary on the hilkhot ha-Rif </title>
                            <title xml:lang="he"> פרוש
                                    הלכות הרי"ף (ערובין)</title>
                            <note>The injured date in the colophon should be read Wednesday, 5146
                                (=1386 CE). This reading is supported by the gematria <foreign xml:lang="he">ה' עוז ל'[ע]'מ'ו' יתן</foreign> at the end of the
                                colophon, as well as by the paper watermarks and the correspondence
                                between the day of the week and the date in the month.</note>
                            <colophon>Partially erased colophon in Aramaic on fol. 83v: <foreign xml:lang="he">"לרבינו ישמעאל זצ"ל ב"ר כבוד ר’ חכמון נ"ע [...?]
                                    בשבתא למנין שלשה ועשרים לירחא דסיון במשנת חמשא אלפין ומא[ה
                                    ואר]בעין ושתא ... ה’ עוז ל’ע’מ’ו’ יתן ... "</foreign>. </colophon>
                            <textLang mainLang="he">Hebrew</textLang>
                        </msItem>
                    </msContents>
